summary: This is a warmup tutorial for TunePad. By the end of this tutorial you'll be making your own music and writing your own code. In this tutorial, we're going to program a simple House beat from scratch. Variants of this beat pattern form the foundation for much of House, EDM, rock, and early hip-hop music.
